    "title": "",
    "depth": 0,
    "paragraphs": [
      {
        "sentences": [
          {
            "text": "Tanks heroes are the most durable among all in Mobile Legends.",
            "formatting": {
              "bold": [
                "Tanks"
              ]
            }
          },
          {
            "text": "These front-line giants help in attacking enemies."
          },
          {
            "text": "They are usually found leading the charge, choosing the right times and situations to initiate aggression."
          },
          {
            "text": "Many tanks can also protect their more fragile teammates by stunning or pushing around dangerous foes and limiting their damage potential.",
            "formatting": {
              "bold": [
                "tanks"
              ]
            }
          },
          {
            "text": "In Mobile Legends, most classes of heroes are really versatile in terms of abilities and with the item crafting variations."
          },
          {
            "text": "A \"tank\" can be played as a DPS if you choose the right equipment.",
            "formatting": {
              "bold": [
                "tank"
              ]
            }
          },
          {
            "text": "Usually, tanks choose to lane on the bottom tower.",
            "formatting": {
              "bold": [
                "tanks"
              ]
            }
          },
          {
            "text": "Tanks have high defense and hitpoints, but low damage.",
            "formatting": {
              "bold": [
                "Tanks"
              ]
            }
          },
          {
            "text": "When used properly, a tank could be the strongest hero in the game.",
            "formatting": {
              "bold": [
                "tank"
              ]
            }
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
